death_helper

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
death_helper -  This method deals with any cute messages you want to print when something dies or, cute things you want to do (like not dieng at all).
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed * death_helper(object thing,
int death)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the thing which killed us
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/combat.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method deals with any cute messages you want to print when
something dies or, cute things you want to do (like not dieng
at all).  It handles the alignment shift due to the killing of
this npc as well.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
make_corpse()

.EP

